Steps to follow:
1) Download flat buffers java project from google's git repository : https://github.com/google/flatbuffers. Add these java files in your project
2) Download CMake and build flatc compiler using following command based on platform you are using.
cmake -G "Unix Makefiles"
cmake -G "Visual Studio 10"
cmake -G "Xcode"
3) create a schema for your data
4) use flatc compiler to compile the schema. This will generate some java classes. Add these java classes in your project and use them for creating flatbuffers.

Follow this tutorial: https://google.github.io/flatbuffers/flatbuffers_guide_tutorial.html